{"tid":926502,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[你必需知道]幾時先有人明白抑鬱症係一種病","createTime":"2018-12-03T13:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T03:28:16.000Z","uid":76542,"like":74,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc11367e6de88d90682e14001c2dab6a0943fa4","tid":926502,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多，先睇睇一個患有腸胃病病人同佢朋友既對話。<br />\n<br />\n朋友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   腸胃病病人=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :個肚好痛呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係呀...好痛...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :你唔好肚痛啦...肚痛唔好架..你唔肚痛你身體就好快冇事架喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我明呀...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :咁你記住唔好再肚痛喇，如果痛既話可以搵我，我會支持你架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :多謝...<br />\n<br />\n等等..翻譯一下<br />\n<br />\n朋友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    抑鬱症既人=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :唔開心呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :係呀...好唔開心...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :你唔好亂諗野啦...愈諗愈唔開心..你唔諗身體就好快冇事架喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :我明呀...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :咁你記住唔好亂諗野喇，如果仲唔開心既話可以搵我，我會支持你架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :多謝<br />\n<br />\n.........似曾相識<br />\n<br />\n聽住！不論你地身邊朋友有冇抑鬱，學左先，有用。<br />\n<br />\n抑鬱症唔係因為諗太多負面野，唔係因為成日亂咁諗野，而係因為哩個係病。<br />\n<br />\n感冒係病，肚痛係病，抑鬱都係病，好正常。<br />\n<br />\n點解係病，<br />\n<br />\n只係因為關大腦內既血清素同去甲腎上腺素等等既事。<br />\n<br />\n食完藥，血清素同去甲腎上腺素等等回復正常，作息慢慢回復正常，生活慢慢回歸正常，最後一切正常。<br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單。食藥，恢復，搞掂，講完。"},{"pid":"342bd464e7ac9ebd79cb2b3a7b1eccdd6a0cde2d","tid":926502,"uid":73509,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:26:38.000Z","msg":"未試過抑鬱既人係唔會明，只會叫你睇開啲。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家都快啲走出抑鬱症既陰霾。"},{"pid":"a678e4f8a1d713f15004650717fa62c285477142","tid":926502,"uid":61281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f344cdc0126c10a5c20b4ebbd31721f7f553a6","tid":926502,"uid":76542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"香港真係好多人抑鬱..."},{"pid":"756e0b75565617d70b97abb05d7313863eba93fe","tid":926502,"uid":182475,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"叫啲人用正向思維根治糖尿"},{"pid":"1409473eb91d99e09b67eb8cb22c705d9e747ada","tid":926502,"uid":140130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"如果冇睇呢個post，我可能死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3aab61d8da22e7e65e435b728dab45ef3b45342","tid":926502,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1409473eb91d99e09b67eb8cb22c705d9e747ada","tid":926502,"uid":140130,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:03:14.000Z","msg":"如果冇睇呢個post，我可能死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:20:25.000Z","msg":"快啲睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加油"},{"pid":"3fd6291145ee143670114657208acb29a501e682","tid":926502,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"有病食藥睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c82a49acd82db569358fdd1287dbb8bcbc6bc3d","tid":926502,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":