>\n咁我應該係叫佢咪食腸胃敏感野，食清d先岩<br />\n咁係肚痛呢個case就根本冇錯 合理晒<br />\n同樣 第2個case都係 諗少d咪係解決方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n引喻失當就當自己岩"},{"pid":"c8227d59a441fc87e91c5c8329fcbde350fb7f6b","tid":926502,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"860df714e0141d6444d2c35fac30324b83e0f208","tid":926502,"uid":139546,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5fc11367e6de88d90682e14001c2dab6a0943fa4","tid":926502,"uid":76542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多，先睇睇一個患有腸胃病病人同佢朋友既對話。<br />\n<br />\n朋友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   腸胃病病人=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :個肚好痛呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係呀...好痛...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :你唔好肚痛啦...肚痛唔好架..你唔肚痛你身體就好快冇事架喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我明呀...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :咁你記住唔好再肚痛喇，如果痛既話可以搵我，我會支持你架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :多謝...<br />\n<br />\n等等..翻譯一下<br />\n<br />\n朋友=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    抑鬱症既人=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :唔開心呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :係呀...好唔開心...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :你唔好亂諗野啦...愈諗愈唔開心..你唔諗身體就好快冇事架喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :我明呀...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :咁你記住唔好亂諗野喇，如果仲唔開心既話可以搵我，我會支持你架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :多謝<br />\n<br />\n.........似曾相識